How to run single node test:

1. Install libfam-atomic1 and libfam-atomic1-dev packages.

2. gcc -o fam_atomic_single_node_test fam_atomic_single_node_test.c -lfam_atomic

3. Run ./fam_atomic_single_node_test

4. Check that the test returned an exit code of 0. If so, the test was successful,
   else the test returned with an error.
